			['NS5A', '6E'] => '---GACGACAAGGAAATATCAGTGGCTGCGGAGTGTCACAGGCCGCCCAGGCCCAAGTTCCCACCTGCACTACCTATATGGGCGAGGCCAGATTACAATCCTCCGCTATTGGAGTCTTGGAAAGCGCCGGATTACGACCCCCCCATCGTGTCGGGGTGTGCGCTGCCCCCAAAAGGGCTGACACCCGTACCCCCGCCTCGACGGAAGAGG---GTCGTAAAGCTCGATGAATCAGCTGCTGCTGAGGCGCTCGCCGAGATGGCCCGGAAATCATTCCCATTGAATCCATCAGAGCCTGAAGAGTCTGGGGTGGGAACCTCCGCCACCTCTACTGACGAGACACCGACTTCTGACGAACCAGACGCACAC---TCCGATGCTGGCTCATATAGCTCCATGCCCCCCCTTGAGGGCGAGCCTGGAGACCCCGACTTAAGTTCGGGA------------------------------------------------------TCATGGTCTACAGTCAGTGAGGATGGCGAGGCTGAAAACGACAGTGTTGTGTGTTGC'.gsub('-','X'),

			['NS5B', '1A'] => '',
